WEBVTT

00:00:05.160 --> 00:00:06.400
P'Dan told me that

00:00:06.400 --> 00:00:07.640
He's going to put these photos

00:00:07.640 --> 00:00:08.680
In an exhibition.

00:00:09.480 --> 00:00:10.520
Did you invite you.

00:00:11.320 --> 00:00:12.400
I wanted to surprise you.

00:00:13.080 --> 00:00:14.240
So I didn't tell you.

00:00:14.240 --> 00:00:15.600
You're unhappy about this, right?

00:00:15.600 --> 00:00:17.200
You put a price on my photos too.

00:00:17.640 --> 00:00:18.880
Can I borrow some money?

00:00:18.880 --> 00:00:19.440
How much?

00:00:19.920 --> 00:00:20.600
1.2 million.

00:00:20.880 --> 00:00:22.320
Do you even realize what you've done?

00:00:23.200 --> 00:00:24.720
Argh!

00:00:31.240 --> 00:00:33.240
Are you in your right mind right now?

00:00:36.400 --> 00:00:38.680
Are you sure you want to do this contract with me?

00:00:39.720 --> 00:00:41.720
The deal where I can ask for anything in return?

00:00:43.840 --> 00:00:44.640
Yes.

00:00:45.320 --> 00:00:46.120
I'll do it.

00:01:18.600 --> 00:01:20.960
Our agreement...

00:01:22.120 --> 00:01:23.760
Is complete.

00:01:26.920 --> 00:01:29.320
I'll never let you go again.

00:03:42.480 --> 00:03:44.320
I've cleared your debt.

00:03:49.000 --> 00:03:50.040
All of it?

00:03:52.200 --> 00:03:53.040
I didn't have to.

00:03:54.000 --> 00:03:56.360
I just destroyed their football betting gang.

00:03:57.120 --> 00:03:58.640
What if they try to get revenge?

00:03:59.360 --> 00:04:00.080
Don't worry.

00:04:02.200 --> 00:04:03.240
You can take your mind off that.

00:04:06.240 --> 00:04:07.720
As for Jet's injuries

00:04:08.160 --> 00:04:10.080
I'll tell your parents

00:04:11.080 --> 00:04:12.760
That I saw Jet getting beat up by some thugs

00:04:12.760 --> 00:04:13.800
Who were trying to steal from him.

00:04:14.600 --> 00:04:15.880
I saw what was happening

00:04:15.880 --> 00:04:16.720
And helped him.

00:04:24.400 --> 00:04:25.200
Sit down.

00:04:36.480 --> 00:04:39.040
Let's talk about our contract.

00:04:43.040 --> 00:04:44.440
Do you remember the terms of the contract?

00:04:48.480 --> 00:04:50.120
That I will belong to only you

00:04:53.560 --> 00:04:55.720
And follow your every rule.

00:04:59.840 --> 00:05:00.640
Rule number one.

00:05:04.600 --> 00:05:06.600
Don't be too emotional.

00:05:08.600 --> 00:05:09.400
I don't like that.

00:05:11.880 --> 00:05:12.680
Rule number two.

00:05:13.640 --> 00:05:15.680
You said you'll belong only to me.

00:05:19.200 --> 00:05:20.880
But words aren't enough.

00:05:24.080 --> 00:05:25.560
You have to show me too.

00:05:30.960 --> 00:05:32.040
Don't cry.

00:05:33.320 --> 00:05:35.400
Didn't I just tell you the first rule?

00:05:36.120 --> 00:05:38.200
Don't be too emotional.

00:06:20.600 --> 00:06:25.040
You walk in with a warning sign

00:06:27.400 --> 00:06:32.520
Just one look and already falling for you

00:06:34.720 --> 00:06:39.840
My friends tell me not to cross that line

00:06:41.880 --> 00:06:47.000
But I’m already out of time

00:06:48.760 --> 00:06:51.120
I know the truth, I taste the sin

00:06:51.120 --> 00:06:52.600
It’s wrong but I don’t want it to be true

00:06:52.600 --> 00:06:55.200
I’m losing all my discipline

00:06:55.200 --> 00:06:59.080
You’re all I’m thinking of

00:06:59.080 --> 00:07:01.200
And I’m breaking all the rules

00:07:01.200 --> 00:07:03.520
Just because

00:07:03.520 --> 00:07:06.800
You’re a red flag but I’m colorblind

00:07:06.800 --> 00:07:10.520
I know you’re dangerous

00:07:10.880 --> 00:07:14.080
If it burns, let it burn me alive

00:07:14.080 --> 00:07:19.080
I can't hold myself back, I’d cross every line

00:07:24.000 --> 00:07:27.400
Ooh

00:07:47.400 --> 00:07:48.040
Jane.

00:07:50.640 --> 00:07:51.440
Jane.

00:07:53.280 --> 00:07:54.000
Jane, how are you?

00:07:54.520 --> 00:07:55.320
I called you so many times,

00:07:55.320 --> 00:07:56.320
Why didn't you pick up?

00:07:57.760 --> 00:07:58.360
So..

00:07:59.000 --> 00:08:00.160
Why did you ask to meet up?

00:08:02.320 --> 00:08:02.920
P'Dan.

00:08:06.760 --> 00:08:07.880
Let's break up.

00:08:11.000 --> 00:08:11.760
Jane.

00:08:13.320 --> 00:08:15.360
You don't really want to break up with me, right?

00:08:16.040 --> 00:08:17.400
He's making you do this right?

00:08:19.640 --> 00:08:21.640
I won't let him force you!

00:08:22.040 --> 00:08:22.800
P'Dan.

00:08:23.400 --> 00:08:24.560
It's not like that.

00:08:27.640 --> 00:08:29.600
I actually wanted to break up with you.

00:08:35.720 --> 00:08:38.039
You're so good to me.

00:08:40.000 --> 00:08:40.840
Do you know

00:08:43.120 --> 00:08:44.960
That if I didn't have you next to me

00:08:49.720 --> 00:08:50.360
I wouldn't have been able to pass through

00:08:50.360 --> 00:08:51.840
Those hard times.

00:08:56.360 --> 00:08:57.520
I really like you.

00:09:00.960 --> 00:09:02.440
But not in that way.

00:09:06.560 --> 00:09:07.320
P'Dan.

00:09:08.800 --> 00:09:10.120
I don't love you.

00:09:12.840 --> 00:09:14.800
The more I know how you feel about me

00:09:16.280 --> 00:09:18.040
The more I don't want to be selfish.

00:09:18.840 --> 00:09:19.560
I can't bear to see you

00:09:19.560 --> 00:09:21.320
Love me while I don't love you.

00:09:22.600 --> 00:09:23.720
Do you understand?

00:09:33.760 --> 00:09:35.200
I really did try.

00:09:37.360 --> 00:09:39.400
But I can't make myself feel that way about you.

00:09:40.400 --> 00:09:41.200
Why?

00:09:43.040 --> 00:09:44.040
Why can't you?

00:09:46.560 --> 00:09:48.080
Because after all this time

00:09:56.360 --> 00:09:58.320
I can't take my mind off P'Jane.

00:10:07.720 --> 00:10:09.760
So let's end this here.

00:10:10.560 --> 00:10:13.400
Please don't let me hurt your feelings anymore.

00:10:14.720 --> 00:10:15.760
I'm sorry.

00:10:17.720 --> 00:10:19.440
It's all my fault.

00:10:26.960 --> 00:10:27.520
Jane.

00:10:28.800 --> 00:10:30.360
You don't have to apologize.

00:10:31.120 --> 00:10:32.880
I'm also in the wrong.

00:10:35.160 --> 00:10:36.880
Ever since the football field incident,

00:10:38.640 --> 00:10:39.600
I knew

00:10:40.080 --> 00:10:41.400
That you didn't like me.

00:10:44.040 --> 00:10:45.080
I've always known

00:10:46.960 --> 00:10:48.840
That you never forgot him.

00:10:50.040 --> 00:10:51.480
Even though I knew it

00:10:52.800 --> 00:10:54.520
I still decided to approach you.

00:11:03.920 --> 00:11:04.720
It's ok.

00:11:20.040 --> 00:11:21.680
I want to give this back to you.

00:11:25.080 --> 00:11:26.800
It's ok, I want you to have it.

00:11:30.360 --> 00:11:31.520
No.

00:11:33.280 --> 00:11:34.160
I want to give it to you.

00:11:34.520 --> 00:11:35.040
Please?

00:11:36.200 --> 00:11:37.680
At least

00:11:38.800 --> 00:11:40.680
When you're unhappy..

00:11:40.680 --> 00:11:41.920
Please don't do this.

00:11:43.360 --> 00:11:44.640
I'll always be here for you.

00:11:45.400 --> 00:11:45.960
Please.

00:11:53.840 --> 00:11:54.440
P'Dan.

00:12:17.400 --> 00:12:18.800
Thank you so much.

00:12:20.200 --> 00:12:20.800
Yeah.

00:12:21.520 --> 00:12:22.720
I truly mean it.

00:12:30.240 --> 00:12:31.240
I'm going to go now.

00:13:07.480 --> 00:13:09.080
What's wrong?

00:13:09.600 --> 00:13:10.800
You look really tired these days.

00:13:12.360 --> 00:13:13.160
Yeah.

00:13:13.920 --> 00:13:15.320
You're also skipping some classes.

00:13:24.520 --> 00:13:25.040
Hey.

00:13:25.240 --> 00:13:26.520
Put? What are you doing?

00:13:30.360 --> 00:13:31.280
What is this scar?

00:13:34.080 --> 00:13:36.160
Did you already sign a contract with him?

00:13:39.480 --> 00:13:41.400
He pressured you into going back to him, didn't he?

00:13:42.880 --> 00:13:44.400
If you're in trouble,

00:13:45.760 --> 00:13:47.320
P'Dan and I can help you.

00:13:47.920 --> 00:13:48.640
Whoa, whoa, whoa.

00:13:48.800 --> 00:13:50.360
P'Jane is forcing Jane?

00:13:50.520 --> 00:13:51.240
And what does P'Dan

00:13:51.240 --> 00:13:52.080
Have to do with any of this?

00:13:55.760 --> 00:13:57.040
Just stay out of my life.

00:13:58.920 --> 00:13:59.720
It's my problem.

00:14:00.760 --> 00:14:01.880
I can handle it myself.

00:14:03.920 --> 00:14:05.520
Why are you always like this?

00:14:05.520 --> 00:14:07.080
Always shutting me out whenever it's about you.

00:14:07.520 --> 00:14:08.680
I never asked you

00:14:09.120 --> 00:14:10.200
To like me.

00:14:10.680 --> 00:14:11.760
But I thought maybe, at least, if it was P'Dan

00:14:12.000 --> 00:14:14.000
It would be good.

00:14:15.680 --> 00:14:16.440
And in the end,

00:14:17.160 --> 00:14:18.160
This is what you chose.

00:14:24.040 --> 00:14:25.760
Do you even still see me as your friend?

00:14:27.320 --> 00:14:28.000
Hey, hey.

00:14:29.480 --> 00:14:30.960
I don't know what you two are fighting about,

00:14:30.960 --> 00:14:31.760
But please.

00:14:33.440 --> 00:14:34.640
Hey! What do you want me to do?

00:14:35.240 --> 00:14:36.560
How are you supposed to help me?

00:14:37.520 --> 00:14:39.520
You can't even save yourself.

00:14:45.320 --> 00:14:46.120
I'm sorry.

00:14:49.640 --> 00:14:51.080
I'm just a loser

00:14:52.000 --> 00:14:53.640
Who's never been able to help you with anything.

00:14:55.640 --> 00:14:57.120
Then from now on, we're done.

00:14:58.400 --> 00:14:59.040
I..

00:14:59.360 --> 00:15:00.720
Won't get involved in your life anymore!!

00:15:10.240 --> 00:15:11.000
Huh...

00:16:04.120 --> 00:16:04.880
Hey.

00:16:06.360 --> 00:16:07.120
Hey!

00:16:08.760 --> 00:16:09.520
Let go!

00:16:09.800 --> 00:16:10.720
Let go!

00:16:11.880 --> 00:16:12.920
Ahhh!

00:16:13.320 --> 00:16:13.880
Ugh!

00:16:13.880 --> 00:16:14.600
P'Jane!

00:16:14.600 --> 00:16:15.600
Argh! Stop!

00:16:16.120 --> 00:16:17.040
P'Jane!

00:16:17.360 --> 00:16:18.560
P'Jane, stop!

00:16:21.880 --> 00:16:23.240
Stay away from my boyfriend.

00:16:26.920 --> 00:16:27.920
Let's talk outside.

00:16:35.440 --> 00:16:36.320
How did you get here?

00:16:36.680 --> 00:16:37.960
What was our agreement, Jane?

00:16:38.520 --> 00:16:39.800
I tried to say no.

00:16:40.600 --> 00:16:41.320
But I was drunk.

00:16:41.760 --> 00:16:42.560
So what?

00:16:44.120 --> 00:16:45.040
You couldn't resist,

00:16:45.360 --> 00:16:46.520
So you just gave in?

00:16:48.080 --> 00:16:49.360
Are you even listening to me?

00:16:50.960 --> 00:16:52.480
I said I didn't give in!

00:16:55.520 --> 00:16:57.080
Next time, I'll be more careful.

00:16:57.680 --> 00:16:58.480
Happy now?

00:17:04.560 --> 00:17:05.200
P'Jane.

00:17:06.839 --> 00:17:08.079
I already promised

00:17:08.440 --> 00:17:09.800
That I'd belong only to you.

00:17:10.079 --> 00:17:11.480
Please stop hurting other people.

00:17:15.920 --> 00:17:17.280
Words aren't enough.

00:17:18.200 --> 00:17:19.440
Prove it to me.

00:17:21.000 --> 00:17:22.079
Prove that you're mine alone.

00:17:24.920 --> 00:17:25.720
Tonight.

00:17:28.079 --> 00:17:28.880
P'Jane...

00:17:29.720 --> 00:17:30.640
What are you doing?

00:17:32.480 --> 00:17:33.280
P'Jane...

00:17:35.920 --> 00:17:36.960
P'Jane, don't.

00:17:37.440 --> 00:17:38.000
P'Jane!

00:17:38.360 --> 00:17:39.480
P'Jane, let go!!

00:17:46.640 --> 00:17:47.400
P'Jane...

00:17:49.400 --> 00:17:49.880
P'...

00:17:52.240 --> 00:17:53.280
P'Jane!

00:17:53.520 --> 00:17:55.040
You're angry right now.

00:17:58.600 --> 00:17:59.400
Then prove it.

00:18:10.920 --> 00:18:12.080
P'Jane!

00:18:22.560 --> 00:18:23.400
P'Jane...

00:18:24.200 --> 00:18:25.000
P'Jane!

00:18:26.600 --> 00:18:28.440
I don't want to sleep with you like this!

00:18:32.320 --> 00:18:32.800
Ow!

00:18:39.520 --> 00:18:40.400
P'Jane...

00:18:41.160 --> 00:18:41.720
Ow!

00:18:57.560 --> 00:18:58.160
P'Jane.

00:18:59.320 --> 00:19:00.320
P'Jane, don't.

00:19:05.360 --> 00:19:06.120
Argh!

00:19:06.320 --> 00:19:07.240
P'Jane!

00:19:42.920 --> 00:19:43.800
Go home!

00:19:45.840 --> 00:19:46.880
Why did you stop?

00:19:48.240 --> 00:19:49.280
Keep going.

00:19:51.040 --> 00:19:51.960
Go ahead!!

00:19:53.400 --> 00:19:54.760
Isn't this me proving it?

00:19:55.280 --> 00:19:56.880
That I belong only to you.

00:20:04.720 --> 00:20:05.800
I told you to leave.

00:20:08.080 --> 00:20:09.960
Before I can't keep my promise.

00:20:11.880 --> 00:20:12.680
What promise?

00:20:16.920 --> 00:20:18.200
If you won't leave,

00:20:18.840 --> 00:20:19.640
Then I will.

00:22:29.400 --> 00:22:30.720
Next pair, if you're ready,

00:22:30.720 --> 00:22:31.520
Please begin.

00:22:51.880 --> 00:22:52.800
Everyone,

00:22:53.280 --> 00:22:56.360
Even though today is the final exam,

00:22:56.640 --> 00:22:58.360
I want all of you

00:22:58.680 --> 00:23:00.920
To relax and stay comfortable.

00:23:01.320 --> 00:23:02.960
Most importantly, you need to...

00:23:03.320 --> 00:23:05.400
Trust your dance partner.

00:23:08.880 --> 00:23:11.200
Do you trust your dance partner?

00:23:11.880 --> 00:23:12.840
I almost did,

00:23:12.840 --> 00:23:13.880
Until you opened your mouth.

00:23:54.160 --> 00:23:54.880
Hey, hey!

00:23:54.880 --> 00:23:55.480
Jane!

00:23:55.480 --> 00:23:56.640
Shit!

00:23:58.200 --> 00:23:59.120
Are you hurt?

00:24:12.200 --> 00:24:13.760
Are you okay, Jane Jennalee?

00:24:14.240 --> 00:24:14.760
I'm okay.

00:24:15.120 --> 00:24:15.640
Mm.

00:24:15.920 --> 00:24:17.720
If you're okay, then keep dancing.

00:25:02.040 --> 00:25:03.320
Hello, Mom. What's up?

00:25:03.960 --> 00:25:05.440
Jane, are you free?

00:25:05.920 --> 00:25:07.360
Can you go pick Jet up for me?

00:25:08.080 --> 00:25:09.280
Jet's not home yet?

00:25:10.120 --> 00:25:12.520
His school activity just ended,

00:25:12.520 --> 00:25:14.120
And he already tried calling for a ride,

00:25:14.120 --> 00:25:15.800
But nobody's accepting it.

00:25:16.840 --> 00:25:17.600
And...

00:25:18.040 --> 00:25:18.800
What about Dad?

00:25:19.520 --> 00:25:20.800
He's busy.

00:25:21.040 --> 00:25:22.480
And it's already late.

00:25:22.920 --> 00:25:25.040
I'm worried some gangsters might hurt Jet

00:25:25.040 --> 00:25:26.400
Or extort money from him again.

00:25:27.240 --> 00:25:28.240
I understand.

00:25:28.760 --> 00:25:30.880
I'll go pick Jet up and take him home myself.

00:25:31.120 --> 00:25:32.120
Thank you, Jane.

00:25:32.680 --> 00:25:33.880
Please look after your brother for me.

00:25:36.120 --> 00:25:36.760
Yes, Mom.

00:26:05.560 --> 00:26:06.360
P'Jane,

00:26:07.640 --> 00:26:09.320
I'm going to pick Jet up from school.

00:26:15.640 --> 00:26:16.480
Come with me.

00:26:37.280 --> 00:26:37.920
Jet.

00:26:38.480 --> 00:26:39.520
Say thank you to P'Jane.

00:26:40.000 --> 00:26:40.920
He came all the way here to pick you up.

00:26:42.240 --> 00:26:43.520
Thank you, P'Jane.

00:26:44.720 --> 00:26:45.640
And...

00:26:46.560 --> 00:26:48.840
This is my way of thanking you

00:26:49.240 --> 00:26:50.840
For helping me before.

00:26:57.720 --> 00:26:58.520
Thanks.

00:27:00.560 --> 00:27:01.120
Jane,

00:27:01.920 --> 00:27:03.440
Can you take that for me?

00:27:21.320 --> 00:27:21.880
Jet,

00:27:22.360 --> 00:27:24.440
Why weren't you more careful?

00:27:37.400 --> 00:27:38.200
Thank you.

00:28:51.680 --> 00:28:53.640
I'll make you an American breakfast.

00:29:02.040 --> 00:29:03.800
Do you still want two fried eggs like usual, Jane?

00:29:09.080 --> 00:29:09.800
Yeah.

00:29:36.600 --> 00:29:37.320
Why are they making us sit through exams

00:29:37.320 --> 00:29:38.440
Until our backs are stiff?

00:29:38.440 --> 00:29:39.680
I seriously don't get it.

00:29:40.120 --> 00:29:41.760
What a waste of a whole day.

00:29:42.040 --> 00:29:43.000
Didn't get to play games,

00:29:43.480 --> 00:29:44.880
Didn't get to play football.

00:29:48.320 --> 00:29:49.400
Did he come to pick you up?

00:29:52.840 --> 00:29:53.760
I guess so.

00:29:55.400 --> 00:29:56.720
Honestly, I don't know

00:29:56.720 --> 00:29:57.960
What he's thinking.

00:29:59.920 --> 00:30:00.480
Hey.

00:30:01.200 --> 00:30:02.640
Are you two back together or what?

00:30:04.240 --> 00:30:06.800
Then why are you still acting like you're fighting?

00:30:09.920 --> 00:30:11.080
I don't know either.

00:30:12.240 --> 00:30:13.480
What we're going through now,

00:30:14.080 --> 00:30:15.200
Does it even count as a fight?

00:30:17.520 --> 00:30:19.720
If you're really going to get back together,

00:30:19.720 --> 00:30:21.120
Then whatever you're keeping inside,

00:30:21.120 --> 00:30:22.280
Say it.

00:30:22.280 --> 00:30:23.520
Before it turns into something bigger.

00:30:29.320 --> 00:30:29.960
Go.

00:30:30.640 --> 00:30:32.840
He's already waiting.

00:30:37.640 --> 00:30:38.520
Good luck, buddy.

00:30:44.840 --> 00:30:45.640
P'Jane.

00:30:56.440 --> 00:30:57.320
Let's go home.

00:31:16.920 --> 00:31:17.440
Hey..

00:31:17.760 --> 00:31:19.000
Can we talk for a minute?

00:31:32.160 --> 00:31:33.920
That promise you mentioned that night...

00:31:35.520 --> 00:31:37.400
Was it the promise you made to me before?

00:31:37.960 --> 00:31:39.640
That if I wasn't ready,

00:31:39.640 --> 00:31:40.680
You wouldn't force me?

00:31:43.000 --> 00:31:43.800
You know,

00:31:44.640 --> 00:31:46.560
I was really angry at you that day.

00:31:48.880 --> 00:31:50.640
You can say it's because you love me,

00:31:51.400 --> 00:31:53.400
But you still had no right to do that to me.

00:31:55.840 --> 00:31:56.640
I'm sorry.

00:31:58.560 --> 00:32:00.240
I promise it won't happen again.

00:32:07.000 --> 00:32:08.440
I'll belong only to you.

00:32:10.040 --> 00:32:11.600
But I want to ask you for one thing.

00:32:13.640 --> 00:32:15.320
I want to know everything you do.

00:32:16.640 --> 00:32:17.720
Your whole life.

00:32:19.560 --> 00:32:20.400
Because I don't want to be with you

00:32:20.400 --> 00:32:21.600
Without knowing anything at all.

00:32:37.400 --> 00:32:38.040
Mm.

00:32:45.640 --> 00:32:46.440
Thank you.

00:33:25.520 --> 00:33:26.520
Why are you here?

00:33:27.920 --> 00:33:29.840
I was out, and I passed by a cake shop.

00:33:30.200 --> 00:33:31.680
So I bought you some cheesecake.

00:33:32.280 --> 00:33:33.640
I remembered you like it.

00:33:48.200 --> 00:33:49.240
I wanted to apologize

00:33:49.640 --> 00:33:51.320
For what I said to you that day.

00:33:56.720 --> 00:33:58.120
I was just really upset

00:33:59.320 --> 00:34:00.840
That I couldn't help you at all.

00:34:09.199 --> 00:34:10.760
I owe you an apology too.

00:34:14.639 --> 00:34:15.520
I know you only did it

00:34:15.520 --> 00:34:16.440
Because you were worried about me.

00:34:16.880 --> 00:34:17.400
Yeah.

00:34:18.040 --> 00:34:19.679
I really was worried about you.

00:34:31.120 --> 00:34:35.440
(P'Jane: I'll come pick you up at the shop.)

00:34:42.440 --> 00:34:44.360
Can we talk another time?

00:34:46.719 --> 00:34:47.600
It's okay.

00:34:48.800 --> 00:34:49.920
Then I'll get going.

00:34:56.040 --> 00:34:56.679
Put.

00:35:02.040 --> 00:35:03.040
Just let it go.

00:35:03.880 --> 00:35:05.600
Whatever that happen before this.

00:35:43.720 --> 00:35:45.080
So where are we going?

00:35:45.920 --> 00:35:48.000
Someone called and asked me for a favor.

00:35:49.240 --> 00:35:50.840
But they wanted to meet in person.

00:35:53.040 --> 00:35:54.480
So I brought you along.

00:35:59.920 --> 00:36:01.600
Have you been doing this for a long time?

00:36:01.880 --> 00:36:02.880
Since high school.

00:36:10.360 --> 00:36:11.680
Why do you do this?

00:36:12.400 --> 00:36:13.680
Does it have something to do with your family?

00:36:16.240 --> 00:36:17.400
I do it for myself.

00:36:19.560 --> 00:36:20.040
And...

00:36:20.400 --> 00:36:21.920
Don't you feel anything at all?

00:36:22.760 --> 00:36:23.640
Having to punish people

00:36:23.640 --> 00:36:24.520
For breaking their promises?

00:36:24.840 --> 00:36:26.240
Why should I feel anything?

00:36:26.720 --> 00:36:27.720
Tee embezzled money,

00:36:28.520 --> 00:36:30.000
He goes to prison, right?

00:36:31.040 --> 00:36:32.320
Jui cheated on her boyfriend

00:36:32.800 --> 00:36:34.440
And stole money from him too.

00:36:35.360 --> 00:36:37.400
One day, her boyfriend was bound to come after her.

00:36:37.960 --> 00:36:39.160
Am I wrong?

00:36:41.680 --> 00:36:43.360
I'm not adding any punishment

00:36:44.000 --> 00:36:46.240
To what they deserved.

00:36:48.640 --> 00:36:49.720
Looks like you think

00:36:50.440 --> 00:36:53.000
What I'm doing is cruel.

00:36:53.000 --> 00:36:54.760
I'm just making an exchange.

00:36:54.760 --> 00:36:56.160
They're the ones

00:36:57.160 --> 00:36:59.200
Who think they can get something for free.

00:37:02.840 --> 00:37:05.080
Then when it's time to pay the price,

00:37:05.080 --> 00:37:06.920
They turn around and call me cruel.

00:37:08.600 --> 00:37:11.400
Do you really think everything you do is right?

00:37:15.760 --> 00:37:16.480
Yes.

00:37:17.600 --> 00:37:19.960
But Tee wasn't fit to be student president.

00:37:20.840 --> 00:37:22.360
If you hadn't made him president in the first place,

00:37:23.560 --> 00:37:24.240
He wouldn't have had the chance

00:37:24.240 --> 00:37:25.560
To steal from everyone.

00:37:27.800 --> 00:37:29.320
A person like that,

00:37:29.640 --> 00:37:30.280
Even if he didn't do it there,

00:37:30.280 --> 00:37:31.000
He would've done it somewhere else.

00:37:31.640 --> 00:37:32.320
True.

00:37:33.600 --> 00:37:34.320
And one day,

00:37:34.920 --> 00:37:37.240
Someone else would've caught him.

00:37:37.880 --> 00:37:38.400
P'Jane,

00:37:38.960 --> 00:37:41.240
You don't have to do this.

00:37:57.840 --> 00:37:58.640
We're here.

00:38:24.280 --> 00:38:26.280
I thought we'd be meeting at your pub.

00:38:26.280 --> 00:38:27.480
I didn't expect

00:38:28.840 --> 00:38:31.040
A place like this.

00:38:32.560 --> 00:38:35.840
Some people aren't comfortable meeting at my pub.

00:38:35.840 --> 00:38:37.280
The ones who like hiding who they are

00:38:38.520 --> 00:38:40.840
Usually prefer places like this.

00:38:52.400 --> 00:38:53.240
Are you here yet?

00:38:53.520 --> 00:38:54.360
Not yet, wait inside first.

00:39:05.760 --> 00:39:06.640
Is something wrong?

00:39:19.400 --> 00:39:20.240
Jane? Hey!

00:39:20.880 --> 00:39:21.360
Hey!

00:39:21.880 --> 00:39:22.360
Hey!

00:39:27.720 --> 00:39:28.320
Jane!

00:39:34.960 --> 00:39:35.480
Huh?

00:39:37.240 --> 00:39:38.080
Wait in the car.

00:39:38.720 --> 00:39:39.720
Start the engine and be ready.

00:39:40.520 --> 00:39:41.360
What about you?

00:39:41.360 --> 00:39:42.520
I'll cover you.

00:39:43.200 --> 00:39:44.640
If I don't make it back within ten minutes,

00:39:44.960 --> 00:39:45.960
Just drive away.

00:39:46.560 --> 00:39:47.720
No, P'Jane.

00:39:48.320 --> 00:39:49.440
Just go.

00:39:49.920 --> 00:39:50.840
If you stay,

00:39:50.840 --> 00:39:52.080
It'll be harder for me to protect you.

00:39:52.080 --> 00:39:53.480
And we'll both end up dead.

00:39:53.920 --> 00:39:54.720
Trust me.

00:39:58.320 --> 00:39:58.800
Go.

00:39:59.720 --> 00:40:00.720
You! Watch out!

00:41:01.920 --> 00:41:02.480
P'Jane!

00:41:03.600 --> 00:41:04.400
P'Jane!

00:41:06.240 --> 00:41:07.040
Are you okay?

00:41:19.840 --> 00:41:21.000
Are you okay?

00:41:24.160 --> 00:41:24.720
P'Jane..

00:41:31.280 --> 00:41:32.320
You've been shot?

00:41:37.240 --> 00:41:37.800
Huh?

00:41:38.400 --> 00:41:39.200
What do I do?

00:41:40.880 --> 00:41:42.520
We need to get out of here.

00:42:15.520 --> 00:42:16.680
P'Jane, stay with me.

00:42:20.560 --> 00:42:21.880
P'Jane, are you okay?

00:42:27.720 --> 00:42:28.840
Who were they?

00:42:30.800 --> 00:42:32.520
Probably one of my old enemies.

00:42:34.280 --> 00:42:35.640
Someone who set me up.

00:42:52.240 --> 00:42:53.320
Hello, Jane?

00:42:54.520 --> 00:42:56.200
I need surgery.

00:42:58.000 --> 00:42:59.000
I've been shot.

00:42:59.440 --> 00:43:00.240
Where are you now?

00:43:02.440 --> 00:43:03.520
We're heading to the hospital.

00:43:04.600 --> 00:43:05.600
Can you make it?

00:43:10.520 --> 00:43:11.440
I'm still hanging on.

00:43:12.120 --> 00:43:14.080
Get here as fast as you can, I'll prepare the operating room.

00:43:16.840 --> 00:43:17.880
Follow the map.

00:43:18.640 --> 00:43:19.440
Okay.

00:43:23.960 --> 00:43:25.360
P'Jane, don't die on me.

00:43:25.680 --> 00:43:26.480
P'Jane...

00:43:26.960 --> 00:43:28.280
P'Jane, please don't die.

00:43:28.280 --> 00:43:29.480
Please wait outside.

00:43:40.800 --> 00:43:41.400
Doctor.

00:43:41.760 --> 00:43:42.400
Doctor!

00:43:42.440 --> 00:43:44.120
Calm down, wait here first.

00:43:44.120 --> 00:43:45.040
I'll take care of everything.

00:43:45.040 --> 00:43:46.280
Please save P'Jane.

00:44:24.160 --> 00:44:24.640
P'...?

00:44:25.000 --> 00:44:26.520
How is P'Jane?

00:44:32.640 --> 00:44:33.680
Don't worry.

00:44:34.240 --> 00:44:35.960
He's out of danger now.

00:44:37.040 --> 00:44:38.920
The bullet may have missed vital organs,

00:44:38.920 --> 00:44:40.520
But he lost a lot of blood.

00:44:40.840 --> 00:44:41.560
Still,

00:44:41.880 --> 00:44:42.640
If you'd arrived any later,

00:44:43.000 --> 00:44:44.120
Things could've been much worse.

00:44:49.160 --> 00:44:50.640
You're Jane Jennalee, right?

00:44:55.240 --> 00:44:56.000
P'Jane

00:44:56.200 --> 00:44:57.600
Told you about me?

00:44:59.760 --> 00:45:00.880
My name's Ram.

00:45:01.320 --> 00:45:03.000
I'm his doctor.

00:45:03.400 --> 00:45:05.360
And his cousin too.

00:45:07.080 --> 00:45:08.120
Nice to meet you.

00:45:08.440 --> 00:45:09.240
Don't worry.

00:45:10.440 --> 00:45:11.800
I talk to him a lot.

00:45:12.800 --> 00:45:14.760
He's told me about you before.

00:45:16.480 --> 00:45:18.040
He talks about me?

00:45:19.280 --> 00:45:20.080
Yeah.

00:45:22.560 --> 00:45:23.240
So..

00:45:23.600 --> 00:45:24.800
Is this your first time dealing

00:45:24.800 --> 00:45:25.640
With something like this?

00:45:29.480 --> 00:45:31.120
He won't be sleeping at the hospital today

00:45:31.600 --> 00:45:33.920
But I want you to watch out for infection.

00:45:34.800 --> 00:45:36.360
Honestly, Jane already knows all this.

00:45:36.880 --> 00:45:38.040
But I'd like to ask you to help

00:45:38.040 --> 00:45:39.240
Take care of his wound.

00:45:39.920 --> 00:45:40.640
Because someone like him

00:45:40.640 --> 00:45:41.280
Would never agree to come to

00:45:41.280 --> 00:45:42.240
A clinic for dressing changes.

00:45:45.680 --> 00:45:46.800
Does P'Jane

00:45:48.040 --> 00:45:50.200
Go through things like this often?

00:45:52.440 --> 00:45:53.240
All the time.

00:45:54.640 --> 00:45:55.200
He's been in situations way

00:45:55.200 --> 00:45:56.000
More dangerous than this.

00:45:58.040 --> 00:45:59.040
Did you know...

00:45:59.480 --> 00:46:00.680
I've actually had to carry surgical equipment

00:46:00.680 --> 00:46:02.080
And operate on him outside a hospital before.

00:46:03.560 --> 00:46:04.560
One day, he's definitely going to turn me

00:46:04.560 --> 00:46:05.960
Into an underground doctor.

00:46:09.040 --> 00:46:10.040
This is the first time

00:46:10.040 --> 00:46:11.200
I've ever been through something like this.

00:46:13.880 --> 00:46:16.840
I don't know if I'll ever get used to it.

00:46:22.480 --> 00:46:23.520
Jane's always dragging people

00:46:23.520 --> 00:46:25.000
Into things like this.

00:46:26.080 --> 00:46:27.120
If you're worried about him,

00:46:28.400 --> 00:46:30.720
Please help talk some sense into him.

00:46:35.520 --> 00:46:37.320
I don't think he'd listen to me either.

00:46:42.480 --> 00:46:43.920
I don't know if you realize it,

00:46:45.320 --> 00:46:47.720
But you're very special to him.

00:46:50.920 --> 00:46:51.800
Really?

00:46:58.840 --> 00:47:00.880
I have to go check on my other patients.

00:47:00.880 --> 00:47:02.440
Visiting hours will start in about half an hour.

00:47:02.640 --> 00:47:04.440
You can see Jane then.

00:47:05.840 --> 00:47:06.800
Thank you.

00:48:14.840 --> 00:48:15.520
P'Jane.

00:48:17.960 --> 00:48:19.120
Are you okay?

00:48:25.600 --> 00:48:27.240
I'm better now.

00:48:29.200 --> 00:48:31.600
Do you know how worried I was about you?

00:48:32.040 --> 00:48:33.200
I was scared.

00:48:34.760 --> 00:48:36.000
I was so scared that...

00:48:37.920 --> 00:48:39.520
I thought you were going to...

00:48:40.240 --> 00:48:41.840
It's okay, Jane.

00:48:42.920 --> 00:48:44.520
I'm safe now.

00:48:46.480 --> 00:48:49.240
Can you stop living like this?

00:49:04.400 --> 00:49:05.600
No.

00:49:10.360 --> 00:49:11.720
Not even if I ask you to?

00:49:15.080 --> 00:49:16.480
No.

00:49:27.000 --> 00:49:28.400
I can't stop.

00:49:29.880 --> 00:49:31.680
I've gone too far to quit now.

00:49:33.480 --> 00:49:35.240
This is my life.

00:49:39.800 --> 00:49:41.960
Then how do you expect me to live with this?

00:49:42.840 --> 00:49:45.000
Watching you live like this every day.

00:49:45.000 --> 00:49:45.800
That's exactly why I never wanted you

00:49:45.800 --> 00:49:47.080
Involved in any of this.

00:49:48.080 --> 00:49:49.720
But you asked me to let you in.

00:49:50.240 --> 00:49:51.880
So I did.

00:49:52.840 --> 00:49:54.480
And you're the only person

00:49:56.640 --> 00:49:58.080
I've ever given this much to.

00:50:06.200 --> 00:50:07.800
So you're really not going to stop?

00:50:18.240 --> 00:50:19.720
If you're choosing this kind of life

00:50:23.440 --> 00:50:25.240
Then I wish you nothing but luck.

00:50:42.440 --> 00:50:43.800
Jane, you can't just abandon me like this.

00:50:44.520 --> 00:50:45.040
Have you forgotten?

00:50:45.720 --> 00:50:46.760
That you owe me.

00:50:47.280 --> 00:50:49.120
I'm never letting you go.

00:50:49.560 --> 00:50:50.840
I can trust you, right?

00:50:51.600 --> 00:50:52.680
If anything happens to you,

00:50:53.520 --> 00:50:54.640
I don't think I can go on.

00:50:55.160 --> 00:50:55.880
Don't worry.

00:50:56.320 --> 00:50:58.240
I won't let anyone lay a finger on you.

00:50:58.720 --> 00:50:59.720
You promised me, right?

00:51:00.240 --> 00:51:01.320
That you'd tell me everything.

00:51:01.840 --> 00:51:03.160
Then I'm going to see my friends tonight.

00:51:03.800 --> 00:51:04.320
Why?!

00:51:04.840 --> 00:51:05.640
Put, calm down.

00:51:06.120 --> 00:51:08.120
Can you please just do what I ask for once? Ow!

00:51:08.680 --> 00:51:09.680
How did you get here?

00:51:10.880 --> 00:51:11.400
Jane.

00:51:11.840 --> 00:51:13.080
I'm really sorry about just now.

00:51:15.520 --> 00:51:16.760
If you ever come near Jane again,

00:51:17.040 --> 00:51:18.320
I won't let you off easy.

00:51:18.600 --> 00:51:19.280
Hello, Jane?

00:51:19.640 --> 00:51:20.720
Get to the hospital right now.

00:51:21.040 --> 00:51:22.400
Put is in the ER room right now.

00:51:38.080 --> 00:51:42.840
You walk in with a warning sign

00:51:44.960 --> 00:51:50.080
Just one look and already falling for you

00:51:52.320 --> 00:51:57.440
My friends tell me not to cross that line

00:51:59.440 --> 00:52:04.560
But I’m already out of time

00:52:06.360 --> 00:52:08.400
I know the truth, I taste the sin

00:52:08.400 --> 00:52:10.000
It’s wrong but I don’t want it to be true

00:52:10.000 --> 00:52:12.640
I’m losing all my discipline

00:52:12.640 --> 00:52:16.640
You’re all I’m thinking of

00:52:16.640 --> 00:52:18.760
And I’m breaking all the rules

00:52:18.760 --> 00:52:21.040
Just because

00:52:21.040 --> 00:52:24.400
You’re a red flag but I’m colorblind

00:52:24.400 --> 00:52:27.760
I know you’re dangerous

00:52:28.280 --> 00:52:31.640
If it burns, let it burn me alive

00:52:31.640 --> 00:52:35.520
I can't hold myself back, I’d cross every line

00:52:35.520 --> 00:52:38.840
You’re a red flag but I’m colorblind

00:52:38.840 --> 00:52:42.480
I’d give up anything for you

00:52:42.480 --> 00:52:46.080
Even if it burns, I'm willing to melt away

00:52:46.080 --> 00:52:50.960
I can't hold myself back, I’d cross every line

00:52:57.480 --> 00:53:00.720
You can paint me with all your darkest sides

00:53:00.720 --> 00:53:04.320
And I’d still wear them like they’re paradise

00:53:04.320 --> 00:53:07.920
If this love is a perfect crime

00:53:07.920 --> 00:53:11.880
Then I’m guilty for life

00:53:11.880 --> 00:53:12.520
You tell me,

00:53:12.520 --> 00:53:16.120
Don’t be too emotional that’s rule no. 1

00:53:16.120 --> 00:53:19.680
I’d give up everything to be your only one

00:53:19.680 --> 00:53:22.760
Ooh

00:53:22.760 --> 00:53:25.760
You’re the only one

00:53:25.760 --> 00:53:27.760
I know the truth, I taste the sin

00:53:27.760 --> 00:53:29.680
It’s wrong but I don’t want it to be true

00:53:29.680 --> 00:53:32.160
I’m losing all my discipline

00:53:32.160 --> 00:53:36.160
You’re all I’m thinking of

00:53:36.160 --> 00:53:38.200
And I’m breaking all the rules

00:53:38.200 --> 00:53:40.360
Just because

00:53:40.360 --> 00:53:43.800
You’re a red flag but I’m colorblind

00:53:43.800 --> 00:53:47.760
I know you’re dangerous

00:53:47.760 --> 00:53:51.160
If it burns, let it burn me alive

00:53:51.160 --> 00:53:54.840
I can't hold myself back, I’d cross every line

00:53:54.840 --> 00:53:58.360
You’re a red flag but I’m colorblind

00:53:58.360 --> 00:54:02.080
I’d give up anything for you

00:54:02.080 --> 00:54:05.480
Even if it burns, I'm willing to melt away

00:54:05.480 --> 00:54:09.800
I can't hold myself back, I’d cross every line

